Spray a large non-stick skillet with no-stick cooking spray. Add sausage, zucchini and corn mixture; cook and stir over medium-high heat for 8 minutes or until vegetables are cooked and sausage is heated through. Stir in black beans, rice, salsa and chili powder. Cook and stir for 5 minutes or until heated through. Sprinkle with cheese and cilantro (if desired); just before serving.